narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: The computers in this school are increasingly obsolete, and this is especially true for the LCD screen machines. PLEASE, PLEASE, PLEASE, put some faster machines on those LCDs.and give them wireless cards.and figure out some way so that we can use the remotes for presentations without affecting screens 30' away.
Resources are never a problem at YSOA.
Everything was made available. I thank the DM staff for providing us with the necessary materials for the final presentation.
The equipment in the 6th floor computer lab definitely needs updating.
